      "text": "N pehz to gahje Moh-\nsus un Aărōns/ un faz-\nzija us Waraü: Taꞥak-\nka tas KUNGS Israëta\nDeews: Atlaid mannuß Lautis/\nka tee man Swehttus warr tur-\nreht Tukfnefi.\n"
