    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad fazzija tee: Tas Eebre-\nerit Deews irr mums fastappis /\nlaid jelle mehs eetan treijo Dee-\nno Sahjumu Tukfnefi / ka mehs\ntam KUNGAM muhfu Dee-\nwain uppurejam/ ka tas pahr\nmums ne nahß ar Mehri/jeb ar\nSohbinu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad fazzija tas Egiptenu\nKehninsch us teem: Juhs Moh-\nsus un Aărōns/ kapehz atraujat\njuhs tohs Lautis no winno Dar-\nbeem? eita pee juhtu Nastahm.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Wehl fazzija Waraüß:\nRedsi/to Lauschu eekßch Semmes\nirr taggad dauds/ un juhs grib-\nbetut tohs no winno Darbein\natraut?\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Waraüß pawehleja tai\nDeena teem Usraugeim/ un teem\nJahtneekeim starp teem Lautim/\nun fazzija:\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Juhs ne buhs jo prohjam\nteem Lautim Salnus doht pee\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un to Keegeko Pu-\ntee zittkahrt irr darrijufch\njuhs teem ta patt uslik\nne buhs no teem ne ko at-\ntee irr bes Darba / tade-\ntee/ un faßka: Eima/ la-\nmuhfu Deewam uppurej\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Latd ta Kalpofcha-\nteem Wihreim gruhtak-\nka teem Darbs effus/ un-\nschahß pee Mellu-Walla\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad isgahje to\nUsraugi un tee Jahtneeki/\nnaja us teem Lautim/\ntmi: Taꞥakka Waraüß\ndohschu jums wairs Sa-\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Eite paschi / d-\njuhs Salmus kur dab-\ntamehr no juhsa Darba\nne kas atlaisis.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad isklihde tee\npa wißßu Egiptes-Seinin\nRuggajus fafrahtu\nweeta.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tee Usraugi spee-\nfazidami: pabeidseet juh-\nnas-Darbu itt ta patt/\njuhs Salini bija.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Israëta Behru-\nneeki/ ko Waraüß Junk-\nteem bij eezehtufchi tapp-\nun tappe fazzihts : Kape-\nfat juhs fawu nospreestu-\npabeigufchi/ Keegetus de-\nmi itt ka papreeßchu/ ta-\nridsan wakkar un fhodee\n"
